title: Dmitri Andreyevich Golubev
text:
Dmitri Andreyevich Golubev (; born 5 January 1985) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er. 
Club career.
He made his debut for <a href="FC%20Shinnik%20Yaroslavl">FC Shinnik Yaroslavl</a> on 3 July 2004 in an <a href="2004%20UEFA%20Intertoto%20Cup">Intertoto Cup</a> game against <a href="FK%20Teplice">FK Teplice</a>.
